; ============================================================================================================
; AutoHotkey (https://www.autohotkey.com/) script for
; mapping Satechi Media Button (http://www.satechi.net/index.php/satechi-bluetooth-button-series-media-button)
; keys to PowerPoint clicker hotkeys 
; ============================================================================================================
Media_Prev::Left		;previous slide
Media_Next::Right		;next slide
Volume_Up::+F5			;start from current slide
Volume_Down::Escape		;end presentation
Media_Play_Pause::b		;black screen
